fr.apteryx.imageio.dicom
Class AERegistry

Object
  AERegistry

public class AERegistry
extends Object

A registry for Application Entities. AE are registered using their names, IP address, port and possible secure transport profile. This registry is used by the QueryRetrieveSCP class to map AE names sent in C-MOVE commands to PeerAE objects.

It is also used by the StorageCommitmentSCP class when it must establish an association with the SCU to send the result of a request.

getPeerAE

public PeerAE getPeerAE(String ae)
Creates a PeerAE from an AE title using the information in the registry. Returns null if the supplied AE title in unknown. The current plugin-wide application title is used as the calling AE title.
